{
  "page_title": "发送普通邮件",
  "apis": [
    {
      "group_title": "发送普通邮件",
      "api_name": "compose_send",
      "method": "POST",
      "api_url": "https://qyapi.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/exmail/app/compose_send?access_token=ACCESS_TOKEN",
      "description": "应用可以通过该接口发送普通邮件，支持附件能力。",
      "query_params": [
        {
          "name": "access_token",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "调用接口凭证"
        }
      ],
      "body_params": [
        {
          "name": "to",
          "type": "object",
          "required": true,
          "description": "收件人，to.emails 和 to.userids 至少传一个"
        },
        {
          "name": "to.emails",
          "type": "string[]",
          "required": false,
          "description": "收件人，邮箱地址"
        },
        {
          "name": "to.userids",
          "type": "string[]",
          "required": false,
          "description": "收件人，企业内成员的userid"
        },
        {
          "name": "cc",
          "type": "object",
          "required": false,
          "description": "抄送"
        },
        {
          "name": "cc.emails",
          "type": "string[]",
          "required": false,
          "description": "抄送人，邮箱地址"
        },
        {
          "name": "cc.userids",
          "type": "string[]",
          "required": false,
          "description": "抄送人，企业内成员的userid"
        },
        {
          "name": "bcc",
          "type": "object",
          "required": false,
          "description": "密送"
        },
        {
          "name": "bcc.emails",
          "type": "string[]",
          "required": false,
          "description": "密送人，邮箱地址"
        },
        {
          "name": "bcc.userids",
          "type": "string[]",
          "required": false,
          "description": "密送人，企业内成员的userid"
        },
        {
          "name": "subject",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "标题"
        },
        {
          "name": "content",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "内容"
        },
        {
          "name": "attachment_list",
          "type": "object[]",
          "required": false,
          "description": "附件相关"
        },
        {
          "name": "attachment_list[].file_name",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "文件名"
        },
        {
          "name": "attachment_list[].content",
          "type": "string",
          "required": true,
          "description": "文件内容（base64编码），所有附件加正文的大小不允许超过50M, 且附件个数不能超过200个"
        },
        {
          "name": "content_type",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "内容类型 html，text（默认是html）"
        },
        {
          "name": "enable_id_trans",
          "type": "uint32",
          "required": false,
          "description": "表示是否开启id转译，0表示否，1表示是，默认0。仅第三方应用需要用到，企业自建应用可以忽略。 目前仅subject、content、attachment_list[].file_name字段支持转译。"
        }
      ],
      "response_params": [
        {
          "name": "errcode",
          "type": "int32",
          "required": false,
          "description": "返回码"
        },
        {
          "name": "errmsg",
          "type": "string",
          "required": false,
          "description": "对返回码的文本描述内容"
        }
      ],
      "request_examples": [
        {
          "title": "请求包体示例",
          "language": "json",
          "code": "{\n    \"to\": {\n        \"emails\": [\n            \"word@bgjkcsqy.wecom.work\",\n            \"jyan1@tiyantest.wang\"\n        ],\n        \"userids\": [\n            \"william\"\n        ]\n    },\n    \"cc\": {\n        \"emails\": [],\n        \"userids\": [\"panyy\"]\n    },\n    \"bcc\": {\n        \"emails\": [\"zoro@bgjkcsqy.wecom.work\"],\n        \"userids\": []\n    },\n    \"subject\": \"这是标题\",\n    \"content\": \"这是邮件正文\",\n    \"attachment_list\": [\n        {\n            \"file_name\": \"a.txt\",\n            \"content\": \"BASE64_CONTENT\"\n        }\n    ],\n    \"enable_id_trans\":1\n}"
        }
      ],
      "response_examples": [
        {
          "title": "返回示例",
          "language": "json",
          "code": "{\n    \"errcode\": 0,\n    \"errmsg\": \"ok\"\n}"
        }
      ],
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "参数说明",
          "content": "to 是收件人，to.emails 和 to.userids 至少传一个\ncc 是抄送\nbcc 是密送\ncontent_type 内容类型 html，text（默认是html）\nenable_id_trans 表示是否开启id转译，0表示否，1表示是，默认0。仅第三方应用需要用到，企业自建应用可以忽略。 目前仅subject、content、attachment_list[].file_name字段支持转译。"
        },
        {
          "title": "id转译模版语法",
          "content": "$departmentName=DEPARTMENT_ID$\n$userName=USERID$\n$userAlias=USERID$\n$userAliasOrName=USERID$\n\n其中 DEPARTMENT_ID 是数字类型的部门id，USERID 是成员账号。\n譬如，\n将$departmentName=1$替换成部门id为1对应的部门名，如“企业微信部”；\n将$userName=lisi007$替换成userid为lisi007对应的用户姓名，如“李四”；\n将$userAlias=lisi007$替换成userid为lisi007对应的用户别名，如“lisi”；\n将$userAliasOrName=lisi007$替换成userid为lisi007对应的用户别名或姓名，别名优先级高于姓名，如\"lisi\"；\n\n若输入的模板不符合语法或无效的userid或者部门ID，则不替换该项内容，保留原样\n转译userAlias时，如果用户没有别名，则不替换该项内容，保留原样\n转译userAliasOrName时，如果用户有别名，则替换为别名；否则，将替换为姓名"
        },
        {
          "title": "权限说明",
          "content": "自建应用需配置到“可调用应用”列表中的应用secret所获取的accesstoken来调用（accesstoken如何获取？）\n第三方应用需具有“邮件”权限\n代开发自建应用需具有“邮件”权限\n`to.userids`/`cc.userids`/`bcc.userids`指定的成员，需在应用的可见范围内"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}